        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1782751681" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6956532897149705664"><br/>This isn&apos;t a biography. This is epic, a novel concept. This is about a seemingly ordinary man and his dreams. How he let his body be crushed but not his dreams. He kept them alive as much as they kept him alive. A family man, a decent person. A happier ending, he made it and got out on his own terms. <br/><br/>This isn&apos;t a biography. This is literature, as close to literature as biographies can get. <br/><br/>Bravo.</span>
  <span id="freeText6956532897149705664" style="display:none"><br />This isn't a biography. This is epic, a novel concept. This is about a seemingly ordinary man and his dreams. How he let his body be crushed but not his dreams. He kept them alive as much as they kept him alive. A family man, a decent person. A happier ending, he made it and got out on his own terms. <br /><br />This isn't a biography. This is literature, as close to literature as biographies can get. <br /><br />Bravo.</span>
