<div id="review_1958570307" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1958570307" />
    <a title="Jay Rain" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/3340837-jay-rain"><img alt="Jay Rain" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1610683685p2/3340837.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1958570307?book_show_action=true">Apr 04, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jay Rain" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jay Rain" href="/user/show/3340837-jay-rain">Jay Rain</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780060392994" href="/book/show/218496.Have_a_Nice_Day_">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1958570307" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2121856649171449727"><b>Rating - 8.3</b><br/><br/>Enough insider information to keep me happy but the impressive part is the dedication/determination that are required if you even want to have a sniff of success; Kudos to Foley for creating a genre<br/><br/>Spawns questions on whether the ephemeral periods of money, power and sex are worth the pain that is endured when it is all gone; Appreciate Mick&apos;s real triple h&apos;s - humour, honesty and humility <br/><br/><br/></span>
  <span id="freeText2121856649171449727" style="display:none"><b>Rating - 8.3</b><br /><br />Enough insider information to keep me happy but the impressive part is the dedication/determination that are required if you even want to have a sniff of success; Kudos to Foley for creating a genre<br /><br />Spawns questions on whether the ephemeral periods of money, power and sex are worth the pain that is endured when it is all gone; Appreciate Mick's real triple h's - humour, honesty and humility <br /><br /><br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="2121856649171449727" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


